examples.korean: He’ll be here soon. 발음듣기 그가 곧 여기 올 거야. Oxford Advanced Learner's English-Korean Dictionary

examples.english: The whole gang will be there. 발음

examples.korean: My date is meeting me at seven. 발음듣기 나와 데이트할 사람이 7시에 날 데리러 올 거야. Oxford Advanced Learner's English-Korean Dictionary

examples.korean: The man’s coming to repair the TV today. 발음듣기 오늘 TV를 고치러 사람[수리공]이 올 거야. Oxford Advanced Learner's English-Korean Dictionary
